i\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"1.2em\" height=\"1.2em\"><path d=\"M2 8.437C2 5.505 4.294 3.094 7.207 3 9.243 3 11.092 4.19 12 6c.823-1.758 2.649-3 4.651-3C19.545 3 22 5.507 22 8.432 22 16.24 13.842 21 12 21 10.158 21 2 16.24 2 8.437z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></span>喜欢</button><div class=\"Popover ContentItem-action\"><button aria-label=\"更多\" id=\"Popover16-toggle\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-owns=\"Popover16-content\" type=\"button\" class=\"Button OptionsButton Button--plain Button--withIcon Button--iconOnly\"><span>​<svg class=\"Zi Zi--Dots Button-zi\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"1.2em\" height=\"1.2em\"><path d=\"M5 14a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4zm7 0a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4zm7 0a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class=\"ModalWrap\"><div class=\"\"></div><div class=\"ModalExp-content\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-content\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-title\">继续浏览内容</div><div class=\"ModalWrap-item\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemImg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-10e18ff65a640175ad058b4b5dfd2867_1440w.png\"></div><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemContent\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemTitle\">知乎</div><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemDesc\">发现更大的世界</div></div><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemBtn\">打开</div></div><div class=\"ModalWrap-item\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemImg\"><img src=\"https://picb.zhimg.com/80/v2-a448b133c0201b59631ccfa93cb650f3_1440w.png\"></div><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemContent\"><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemTitle\">Chrome</div></div><div class=\"ModalWrap-itemBtn\">继续</div></div></div></div></div><div><div class=\"\"></div><div class=\"ModalLoading-content\"><svg width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"CircleLoadingBar\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><g><circle class=\"path\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"30\"></circle></g></svg></div></div></div></div><div class=\"List-item\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"ContentItem AnswerItem\" data-zop=\"{\" authorname\":\"烟霞相许\",\"itemid\":70681110,\"title\":\"有什么好玩的手机游戏？\",\"type\":\"answer\"}\"=\"\" name=\"70681110\" itemprop=\"answer\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Answer\" itemscope=\"\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"AnswerItem\" data-za-extra-module=\"{\" card\":{\"has_image\":false,\"has_video\":false,\"content\":{\"type\":\"answer\",\"token\":\"70681110\",\"upvote_num\":5603,\"comment_num\":455,\"publish_timestamp\":null,\"parent_token\":\"23539361\",\"author_member_hash_id\":\"af3e427c491806613f9194b181b87d42\"}}}\"=\"\"><div class=\"ContentItem-meta\"><div class=\"AuthorInfo AnswerItem-authorInfo AnswerItem-authorInfo--related\" itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"><span class=\"UserLink AuthorInfo-avatarWrapper\"><div class=\"Popover\"><div id=\"Popover21-toggle\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-owns=\"Popover21-content\"><a class=\"UserLink-link\" data-za-detail-view-element_name=\"User\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"//www.zhihu.com/people/yan-xia-xiang-xu\"><img class=\"Avatar AuthorInfo-avatar\" width=\"38\" height=\"38\" src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/740e9a737e6eadd262bc2f6a665aee6c_xs.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" srcset=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/740e9a737e6eadd262bc2f6a665aee6c_l.jpg?source=1940ef5c 2x\" alt=\"烟霞相许\"></a></div></div></span><div class=\"AuthorInfo-content\"><div class=\"AuthorInfo-head\"><span class=\"UserLink AuthorInfo-name\"><div class=\"Popover\"><div id=\"Popover22-toggle\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-owns=\"Popover22-content\"><a class=\"UserLink-link\" data-za-detail-view-element_name=\"User\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"//www.zhihu.com/people/yan-xia-xiang-xu\">烟霞相许</a></div></div></span></div><div class=\"AuthorInfo-detail\"><div class=\"AuthorInfo-badge\"><div class=\"ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText\">诗酒花茶／附庸风雅／不怎么玩游戏了</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"css-h5al4j\"><span class=\"Voters\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"Button Button--plain\">5,603 人赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><div class=\"RichContent RichContent--unescapable\"><div class=\"RichContent-inner RichContent-inner--collapsed\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText\" itemprop=\"text\"><p>【2016.1.22】又更了一点_(:з」∠)_<br>【2016.4.26】第二张图增加了一些<br>【2016.11.28】又增加了一些，然后另外单独安利一个解谜游戏，可以拉到最后。回答过千赞了还涨了点粉，不过答主无干货也少答题，关注需谨慎hhhhh<br>【2017.1.30】统一回复一下用什么下载，因为这是安卓的，所以下一个应用汇或者Taptap，或者直接百度就可以下了。<br>【2017.3.15】看到有评论说建议研发用网线的手机有利青少年身体健康……我……就又更了一点点_(:з」∠)_顺便换了字体。<br>【2017.4.14】原题目为有什么好玩的手机游戏，不知道为什么加了一个“简单”，那恕我直言为何不去玩连连看？<br>【2017.4.20】又更新了一点。<br>【2017.5.13】更新了一个游戏。<br>【2017.7.12】有人问我是不是收费了……不想废话(눈_눈)<br>【2018.2.24】我居然更新了。。。答主大学清心寡欲不怎么玩游戏了（真诚脸），以后有空重新编辑一下回答hhhh</p><p>【2018.7.19】对不起我又更新了Ծ‸Ծ但是没有另外传图，就在第二张图的收藏二里，机械迷宫往后的几个游戏，真的非常非常棒，玩了不亏 </p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p>首先要说一下，大型游戏少，大多数是小众的游戏。直接放图，文末有最近玩的几个游戏的单独推荐。<br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7be62f8e8331c638e66e67873be215c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"2922\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e7be62f8e8331c638e66e67873be215c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e7be62f8e8331c638e66e67873be215c_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"2922\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e7be62f8e8331c638e66e67873be215c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7be62f8e8331c638e66e67873be215c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef53b12f5aa7df638e91855d5a4f253e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"671\" data-rawheight=\"4096\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-edf4c3bdf7075e79e4ca558eac01c7ef_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"671\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ef53b12f5aa7df638e91855d5a4f253e_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ef53b12f5aa7df638e91855d5a4f253e_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"671\" data-rawheight=\"4096\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-edf4c3bdf7075e79e4ca558eac01c7ef_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"671\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ef53b12f5aa7df638e91855d5a4f253e_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef53b12f5aa7df638e91855d5a4f253e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p><br>有些也许不是那么有意思但是我好像品位猎奇...</p><p><br>这里再单独安利一个游戏，复制品（搜索Replica就好）。你作为主角被政府请来破解一个犯罪青年人的手机，单单一个开始就够吸引人了：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-16953d7a97df4c33ad161c12d573eed4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-16953d7a97df4c33ad161c12d573eed4_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-16953d7a97df4c33ad161c12d573eed4_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-16953d7a97df4c33ad161c12d573eed4_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-16953d7a97df4c33ad161c12d573eed4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p><br>进入之后只有这个界面，我试着打开手机，但是不知道密码。然后我看到了短信：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fdd55d617d5bf406c9dd933732528ba5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fdd55d617d5bf406c9dd933732528ba5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-fdd55d617d5bf406c9dd933732528ba5_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fdd55d617d5bf406c9dd933732528ba5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fdd55d617d5bf406c9dd933732528ba5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>嗯，手机主人生日啊，那估计是11.5号。然后我输入1105果然打开了。</p><p>嗯，更多精彩内容赶紧自己下一个慢慢体会hhhhhh</p><p>【3.15】<br>另外最近我迷上一个国产文字rpg，感觉是难得的精品游戏呢。喜欢地下城堡或者妖怪手帐的一定会很喜欢这个游戏的。不多说了我就放两张图大家感受一下。<br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d77567352782d4d85faeb6eb6d24d82_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d77567352782d4d85faeb6eb6d24d82_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d77567352782d4d85faeb6eb6d24d82_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d77567352782d4d85faeb6eb6d24d82_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d77567352782d4d85faeb6eb6d24d82_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-562e7e2871ea41a782b1d849d41736b5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-562e7e2871ea41a782b1d849d41736b5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-562e7e2871ea41a782b1d849d41736b5_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-562e7e2871ea41a782b1d849d41736b5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-562e7e2871ea41a782b1d849d41736b5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>这个游戏叫放置江湖，说来文字模拟游戏真的非常有意思，对这类游戏有兴趣的话可以去搜索一下文字mud_(:з」∠)_</p><p>【4.20】<br>好！猎奇的我！终于对一个非常少女的游戏动了心！<br>这两天沉迷小哥哥……扶我起来我还能肝！<br>主角叫如月晴人，真是很好听的名字啊www</p><p>算是一个剧情向的游戏，不是枯燥的养成，总之实在是非常好玩……我都不知道应该怎么介绍了_(:з」∠)_不发剧情了，想玩的人肯定会看到就去玩的(ง •̀_•́)ง</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-02dcbc810c47802cb132ef36c2a3e2f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-02dcbc810c47802cb132ef36c2a3e2f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-02dcbc810c47802cb132ef36c2a3e2f1_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-02dcbc810c47802cb132ef36c2a3e2f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-02dcbc810c47802cb132ef36c2a3e2f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p><br>这个游戏叫【囚われのパルマ】翻译为【被囚禁的掌心】，也有叫【被囚禁于手中的你】的。出了个续作，不过主人公长得像是个牛郎23333<br>【玩过续作之后的打脸：晴人是我儿子葵才是男朋友_(:з」∠)_】<br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-006f5106042d4c24770d8f52a578aabf_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-006f5106042d4c24770d8f52a578aabf_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-006f5106042d4c24770d8f52a578aabf_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-006f5106042d4c24770d8f52a578aabf_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-006f5106042d4c24770d8f52a578aabf_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2b2da7265ad8cb601baf61615ffc0f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c2b2da7265ad8cb601baf61615ffc0f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c2b2da7265ad8cb601baf61615ffc0f1_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c2b2da7265ad8cb601baf61615ffc0f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2b2da7265ad8cb601baf61615ffc0f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p><br>【5.13】<br>江湖X：汉家江湖</p><p>又是一个武侠类游戏，探险rpg，好玩得不行，人物设定也很棒，而且非常有槽感【误】，玩了就停不下来，缺点是伤肝。<br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ebbd9a57d014fc94ae8c1e3e9f8265d_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3ebbd9a57d014fc94ae8c1e3e9f8265d_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3ebbd9a57d014fc94ae8c1e3e9f8265d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3ebbd9a57d014fc94ae8c1e3e9f8265d_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ebbd9a57d014fc94ae8c1e3e9f8265d_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cbc6fd70e5c294218e370f8eb2c4eea_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8cbc6fd70e5c294218e370f8eb2c4eea_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8cbc6fd70e5c294218e370f8eb2c4eea_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8cbc6fd70e5c294218e370f8eb2c4eea_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cbc6fd70e5c294218e370f8eb2c4eea_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9cce4b54bd113e09152c47784a02ea02_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9cce4b54bd113e09152c47784a02ea02_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9cce4b54bd113e09152c47784a02ea02_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9cce4b54bd113e09152c47784a02ea02_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9cce4b54bd113e09152c47784a02ea02_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-82001fab4d45ef91caa6bf6b1302b7b4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-82001fab4d45ef91caa6bf6b1302b7b4_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-82001fab4d45ef91caa6bf6b1302b7b4_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-82001fab4d45ef91caa6bf6b1302b7b4_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-82001fab4d45ef91caa6bf6b1302b7b4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p><br>这里表白被人吐槽废柴的张少爷，明明输出超高！技能也很可爱(๑• . •๑)</p><p><br>【2018.2.24】没想到我又来了<br>苍之纪元</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d5f73a5c68030d61a9394e5ce370a4ea_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d5f73a5c68030d61a9394e5ce370a4ea_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5f73a5c68030d61a9394e5ce370a4ea_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d5f73a5c68030d61a9394e5ce370a4ea_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d5f73a5c68030d61a9394e5ce370a4ea_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-99346e45f41088ad829d772f738e2a09_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-99346e45f41088ad829d772f738e2a09_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-99346e45f41088ad829d772f738e2a09_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-99346e45f41088ad829d772f738e2a09_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-99346e45f41088ad829d772f738e2a09_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-95428b83b44aade499fb221232168049_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95428b83b44aade499fb221232168049_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-95428b83b44aade499fb221232168049_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95428b83b44aade499fb221232168049_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-95428b83b44aade499fb221232168049_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>回合制放置收集冒险游戏（好长的形容hhh），槽点和优点一样多，出卡率非常良心，画风好看，声优都是大佬（香菜钉宫顺子……），但是语音不够多</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>',5,0,0,1,1,1,'202