paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-56a7479b2cfea7a6b5596354215eac78_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1463\" data-rawheight=\"912\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-340871006df607956d9a6b3f2253e9dd_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1463\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56a7479b2cfea7a6b5596354215eac78_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-56a7479b2cfea7a6b5596354215eac78_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1463\" data-rawheight=\"912\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-340871006df607956d9a6b3f2253e9dd_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1463\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56a7479b2cfea7a6b5596354215eac78_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-56a7479b2cfea7a6b5596354215eac78_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f2207b2b544f045112709d41479d4d2_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"686\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3a3b2cfeafe1213c3900c48811f9c82_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5f2207b2b544f045112709d41479d4d2_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5f2207b2b544f045112709d41479d4d2_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"686\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3a3b2cfeafe1213c3900c48811f9c82_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5f2207b2b544f045112709d41479d4d2_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f2207b2b544f045112709d41479d4d2_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3082b314e7ddd85ee18eaed14320534f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bb3474295965dde1d4b48fcaebaeacac_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3082b314e7ddd85ee18eaed14320534f_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bb3474295965dde1d4b48fcaebaeacac_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3082b314e7ddd85ee18eaed14320534f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p>以下为原回答</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p>1.文豪野犬，这是和文学作品超能力有关的动漫，为野犬干杯！（我抱走太宰治！！！）</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b429dacfcb998a1f6335ee969df66885_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"845\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d7bc6203a8fe7b503fa97f5a0d0855f4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b429dacfcb998a1f6335ee969df66885_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b429dacfcb998a1f6335ee969df66885_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"845\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d7bc6203a8fe7b503fa97f5a0d0855f4_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b429dacfcb998a1f6335ee969df66885_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b429dacfcb998a1f6335ee969df66885_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>2.动物狂想曲，食草动物和肉食动物和平相处下的危机</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b9de74d69e1478ba4dc9544507b52eb_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2244\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c778fe4dc84ec918ea5b6e13f0f8ed52_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2244\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8b9de74d69e1478ba4dc9544507b52eb_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8b9de74d69e1478ba4dc9544507b52eb_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2244\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c778fe4dc84ec918ea5b6e13f0f8ed52_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2244\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8b9de74d69e1478ba4dc9544507b52eb_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b9de74d69e1478ba4dc9544507b52eb_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>3.overlord，骨王装逼篇，罪域的骨终为王！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-45cbbf7701cfb66eacb3d56f7a51d4f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"420\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ebe2a6a4a0fa4b659686e4779c3e9086_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45cbbf7701cfb66eacb3d56f7a51d4f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-45cbbf7701cfb66eacb3d56f7a51d4f1_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"420\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ebe2a6a4a0fa4b659686e4779c3e9086_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-45cbbf7701cfb66eacb3d56f7a51d4f1_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-45cbbf7701cfb66eacb3d56f7a51d4f1_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>4.关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事，萌王装逼篇</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-21fb4a5d508d9d1182e5b3f40a9d9a46_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"719\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-043bba87967ce403ee58207bf700e7b3_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-21fb4a5d508d9d1182e5b3f40a9d9a46_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-21fb4a5d508d9d1182e5b3f40a9d9a46_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"719\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-043bba87967ce403ee58207bf700e7b3_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-21fb4a5d508d9d1182e5b3f40a9d9a46_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-21fb4a5d508d9d1182e5b3f40a9d9a46_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>5.从零开始的异世界（雷姆我也抱走）</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1c958225e69a9355de9d898e3e73d61c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2fb0a1491ab0e44f0094c716c842434a_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic2