ta-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-97353e36948f423f8b3de49720d75c8b_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3372185dd9b1ed608a7de8d1b502e447_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'1920\' height=\'1080\'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-97353e36948f423f8b3de49720d75c8b_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3372185dd9b1ed608a7de8d1b502e447_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3372185dd9b1ed608a7de8d1b502e447_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"></figure><p>39.欢迎来到实力至上主义教室，推理番，安利！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3a54830564c9ef9ba6f0b348899b97e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-241f2209ecd8fe3c68a3f1949ba57d49_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b3a54830564c9ef9ba6f0b348899b97e_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"360\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-241f2209ecd8fe3c68a3f1949ba57d49_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b3a54830564c9ef9ba6f0b348899b97e_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3a54830564c9ef9ba6f0b348899b97e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"></figure><p>40.驱魔少年</p><p>41.钢之炼金术师，经典了，基本上排名必是前十的</p><p>42.进击的巨人，现在小破站没有</p><p>43.东京喰种，小破站也没有</p><p>44.黑执事，经典动漫</p><p>45.六花的勇者</p><p>46.精灵使的剑舞</p><p>47.学战都市</p><p>48.妖怪旅馆营业中，enmmm这个应该定义为美食番，和吃脱不了关系</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-acf59a460e56c878fd3a36789cc7ae1c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"625\" data-rawheight=\"786\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0913db0df448717254d58bcebd54540_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"625\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-acf59a460e56c878fd3a36789cc7ae1c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-acf59a460e56c878fd3a36789cc7ae1c_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"625\" data-rawheight=\"786\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0913db0df448717254d58bcebd54540_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"625\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-acf59a460e56c878fd3a36789cc7ae1c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-acf59a460e56c878fd3a36789cc7ae1c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>49.初恋这件小事，</p><p>50.<b>宝石之国，这个番，画风超级棒</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-90822b92812a477cad0cc5ac0f784cb0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1198\" data-rawheight=\"749\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f21af439f596bceaf121b7e888fece76_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1198\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90822b92812a477cad0cc5ac0f784cb0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'1198\' height=\'749\'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1198\" data-rawheight=\"749\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f21af439f596bceaf121b7e888fece76_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1198\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90822b92812a477cad0cc5ac0f784cb0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-90822b92812a477cad0cc5ac0f784cb0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"></figure><p>51.圣杯，——<b>fate ，非常有名了</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9b40d3f3433deabe8791d9f9e354a7ee_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ee08b4fabf52ec05dffac74ae05081d_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9b40d3f3433deabe8791d9f9e354a7ee_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'1920\' height=\'1080\'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ee08b4fabf52ec05dffac74ae05081d_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9b40d3f3433deabe8791d9f9e354a7ee_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9b40d3f3433deabe8791d9f9e354a7ee_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"></figure><p>52.我想吃掉你的胰脏</p><p>53.魔鬼恋人</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7c9a6a198776dc6c34e40084788e2338_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"375\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-63ab546448156123ae311c280027c824_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7c9a6a198776dc6c34e40084788e2338_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c9a6a198776dc6c34e40084788e2338_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"375\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-63ab546448156123ae311c280027c824_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7c9a6a198776dc6c34e40084788e2338_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7c9a6a198776dc6c34e40084788e2338_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>54.兄弟战争，女主的后宫动漫，各种类型的男生随便挑！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b7c4fdf29895d48a1227d7daab45bc9_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"700\" data-rawheight=\"419\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-95ac7acc1ebb1a279aa092ba75b813d5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"700\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7b7c4fdf29895d48a1227d7daab45bc9_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7b7c4fdf29895d48a1227d7daab45bc9_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"700\" data-rawheight=\"419\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-95ac7acc1ebb1a279aa092ba75b813d5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"700\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7b7c4fdf29895d48a1227d7daab45bc9_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b7c4fdf29895d48a1227d7daab45bc9_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>55.你的名字</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ed6062f0fbad559e0f053ea359d5630_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"1334\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a65fd3f09383660c47df3e2c05922082_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ed6062f0fbad559e0f053ea359d5630_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5ed6062f0fbad559e0f053ea359d5630_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"1334\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a65fd3f09383660c47df3e2c05922082_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ed6062f0fbad559e0f053ea359d5630_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ed6062f0fbad559e0f053ea359d5630_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>56.<b>萤火之森</b>，非常催泪</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ea2bcaa31d028f3e357f556ac6df83c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"720\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-22e1447d0cd014986394bb6d36665f72_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0ea2bcaa31d028f3e357f556ac6df83c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-0ea2bcaa31d028f3e357f556ac6df83c_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"720\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-22e1447d0cd014986394bb6d36665f72_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0ea2bcaa31d028f3e357f556ac6df83c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ea2bcaa31d028f3e357f556ac6df83c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>57魔法少女小圆，从某种意义上我jio得有点像小樱</p><p>58.百变小樱，既然提了，那就说一下吧</p><p>59.摇曳庄的幽奈</p><p>60.潘多拉之心，黑兔子魔女</p><p>61<b>声之形，非常治愈的，当你面对那些与我们不同的人，你会怎么做？</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6cd6b7ff511f028c42ddfa6f63d46da0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-293120572a2a4787df12a0c20d70f2b7_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6cd6b7ff511f028c42ddfa6f63d46da0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'1920\' height=\'1080\'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-293120572a2a4787df12a0c20d70f2b7_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6cd6b7ff511f028c42ddfa6f63d46da0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6cd6b7ff511f028c42ddfa6f63d46da0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"></figure><p>62.哈尔的移动城堡，宫崎骏的都是经典了，比如千与千寻，魔女宅急便，龙猫自行搜索嗷</p><p>63.Hand Shakers 握手者，似乎不太出名，但我追过这个番，画风还不错</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed1397080fdbd0fd489c346c81aedb79_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"677\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-59fa1a5537df5e7630bad3c997e800ad_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed1397080fdbd0fd489c346c81aedb79_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed1397080fdbd0fd489c346c81aedb79_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"677\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-59fa1a5537df5e7630bad3c997e800ad_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ed1397080fdbd0fd489c346c81aedb79_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed1397080fdbd0fd489c346c81aedb79_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>64.为美好的世界献上祝福</p><p>65.玉子市场，著名的情头出处，但是是个正经八门的治愈番</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c33635e80076c3d1007ce6363f0756d5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"619\" data-rawheight=\"576\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3e0979bbe6a58ee10f71251c2a4bd80f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"619\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c33635e80076c3d1007ce6363f0756d5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c33635e80076c3d1007ce6363f0756d5_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"619\" data-rawheight=\"576\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3e0979bbe6a58ee10f71251c2a4bd80f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"619\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c33635e80076c3d1007ce6363f0756d5_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c33635e80076c3d1007ce6363f0756d5_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>66.月刊少女野崎君，著名情头出处+1，是个治愈番，有点和暴走邻家相似。可惜男主是个钢铁直男</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-76395a42d2120c562b6129c30e0f7a36_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-53db534c77eaac06b86c25523b2bd82f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76395a42d2120c562b6129c30e0f7a36_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-76395a42d2120c562b6129c30e0f7a36_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-53db534c77eaac06b86c25523b2bd82f_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76395a42d2120c562b6129c30e0f7a36_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-76395a42d2120c562b6129c30e0f7a36_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>67.终结的炽天使，双男主动漫，不要妄想有女主了</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2fe715df83cf14f2b4d44f5fa2f5031_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1200\" data-rawheight=\"1894\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4df161294df832690e317108975e887_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1200\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f2fe715df83cf14f2b4d44f5fa2f5031_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f2fe715df83cf14f2b4d44f5fa2f5031_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1200\" data-rawheight=\"1894\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4df161294df832690e317108975e887_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1200\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f2fe715df83cf14f2b4d44f5fa2f5031_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2fe715df83cf14f2b4d44f5fa2f5031_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>68，碧蓝航线，关于海上航母的，说实话我对这个题材不感兴趣，但是对这里的女性非常有兴趣，这个动漫大概只有女性，同样也别妄想有男主了，可以一饱眼福，有兽耳娘也有波霸，对A，御姐，萝莉，个人站凰，鸾这对</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-53474ad4a96bc918f91273b9650f51ec_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ad4e958baecd9a337fca45bb4fc525a_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53474ad4a96bc918f91273b9650f51ec_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-53474ad4a96bc918f91273b9650f51ec_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ad4e958baecd9a337fca45bb4fc525a_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53474ad4a96bc918f91273b9650f51ec_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-53474ad4a96bc918f91273b9650f51ec_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>69.平凡职业造就世界最强，神似史莱姆，那个番，但是远远不及</p><p>70.幻界战线，男主眼睛超能力</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-45e7b25e1f80e40fd20e2c0a2cdae0b0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87e02a90464b71067359c2c0e8c73e42_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-45e7b25e1f80e40fd20e2c0a2cdae0b0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-45e7b25e1f80e40fd20e2c0a2cdae0b0_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"2163\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87e02a90464b71067359c2c0e8c73e42_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2163\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-45e7b25e1f80e40fd20e2c0a2cdae0b0_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-45e7b25e1f80e40fd20e2c0a2cdae0b0_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>71.火影忍者，海贼王，无数少男的童年</p><p>72.一拳超人，我变秃了也变强了</p><p>73.爱神巧克力，国产恋爱后宫番</p><p>74.狐妖小红娘，知名国产动漫</p><p>75.画江湖之不良人，18禁~话说其实日漫好多都是18禁吧</p><p>76.四月是你的谎言</p><p>77.未闻花名</p><p>78.有一个动漫是和卡牌有关的，我忘了名字了，只记得最后出现了创造了这个游戏的女生的名字叫茧，然后说什么颜色的时候女主回答的是无色，(啊啊啊真想不起来了有人知道的话告诉我一下吧太痛苦了)</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p>有人告诉我了！是选择感染者！！！！！！</p><p>79.斩赤红之瞳</p><p>80.灼眼的夏娜（这个和上面的我有点分不清了，滴滴——记忆出现混乱）</p><p>81.巧克力和香子兰，猫耳娘！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a1998ce5932fd2bebbebc892f44d8675_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1396\" data-rawheight=\"873\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c1226a15f26181aacc144adb656ff34_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1396\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1998ce5932fd2bebbebc892f44d8675_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-a1998ce5932fd2bebbebc892f44d8675_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1396\" data-rawheight=\"873\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c1226a15f26181aacc144adb656ff34_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1396\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a1998ce5932fd2bebbebc892f44d8675_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a1998ce5932fd2bebbebc892f44d8675_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></figure><p>82.盾之勇者</p><p>83·命运石之门</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c8307228ef90930a166a6f21400c9df6_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3469e24d98287ea8e0918496497a695_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c8307228ef90930a166a6f21400c9df6_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c8307228ef90930a166a6f21400c9df6_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4